<br>
(1) Class Balance for the EXP grp.<br>
<br>
We are Balanced, we have the ability to cause more damage to 3 or 4 mobs in a row than any other class, if your worried about aggro, take the time and get the concussion spell.<br>
<br>
I have heard time and again that wizards suck in exp grps, this is a rumore that unfortunately most of the community beleives, its not founded on any fact, its founded on misperceived observations.<br>
<br>
Let us take a Hypothetical exp grp, 3 tanks 1 cleric, 1 enchanter and a wizard.<br>
<br>
Puller brings in a mob and all three tanks engage, cleric is ready to heal, and enchanter is slow/mez.  Wizard is sitting on his ass medding cause there no f00king way a wizzard is gonna nuke as soon as mob is pulled an get aggro.<br>
<br>
Now here is the thing, for the entire first minute of the fight the wizard is just sitting down while the tanks are working the mob, when mob hits 60% hp wizard stands and starts to Nuke.  Wizard will do approx 40% ofthe mobs hp in damage, the 3 tanks did a combined total of 60%, or 20% each.<br>
<br>
Result?  wizard kicked ass, but because he is &quot;perceived&quot; to have done nothing and thereby contribut NO value we get a bum rap.<br>
<br>
To be fair, every 10 mobs we need to sit out and med cause our mana is Finite.  But we are very well balanced in an exp grp.<br>
<br>
(2) Uber Mob encounters<br>
<br>
Kunark Uber Mobs:  Dont have a lot of casters?  Your screwed unless your tanks are &quot;extremely&quot; well equipped.  From Trakanon Raids i have led and participated in, I would get off anywhere between 5 and 10 Lure of Ice spells, yes thats from 4k to 8k in damage to a fight.  When 20+ peeps are beating on a Mob 1 PC having the capability to cause 13% - 25% of mobs HP damage is damn nice.<br>
<br>
Same is true for all other Kunark Mobs.  One Notable exception is Venril Sathire, he can be done with tank classes only if needed.<br>
<br>
As for VP, dont even bother going unless ye have LOTS of casters that can Nuke down a Mob Fast.<br>
<br>
Veliouse Mobs:  Here is where it gets different, as is well known thesemobs have HUGE amounts of HP, and quite frankly untill ye get your Bane line of spells your not going to be very usefull in a Raid.  Using CT as an example I could usually get anywhere between 12-14k in damage on him, most Rogues and Rangers can do better in a CT fight (True Shot is just fucking awsome heh).  Dain is the same story.  But on the OTHER mobs that can be affected by Banes, or Sunstrike we just rule.  The Typical Vulak Fight I do 50k Damage, thats WAY more than any other class, same is true for other mobs (just not as high damage due to lower hp of those mobs).<br>
<br>
(3) Wizard Gear<br>
<br>
The one thing I notice is that wizards spend alot of effort trying to get AC/HP gear.  For the life of me i dont understand that.  We are a MANA class only. HP and AC is Useless to us, we dont need it.  Focus on getting your int to 255 and getting as many +mana Items as you can.  More Mana = More Nukes, More Int = Higher chance your specialisation will kick in reducing Cost of Nuke and fewer fizzles.<br>
<br>
Work on the concussion spell, its frigging invaluable to us in case of overburn.<br>
<br>
Just my thoughts as the Oldest wizard on this server =)<br>
